Last Congress, my colleagues & I worked tirelessly with @POTUS & the Secretary of VA to make needed reforms to ensure our veterans come first. A 2016 Commission on Care report highlighted problems @ VA & provided solutions which were incorporated into the bipartisan MISSION Act.

VA budget has increased from $97 billion in 2009 to the president's request of $220 billion for FY 2020. If we are wanting to privatize VA & decrease its budget, we are doing a terrible job. No president in my lifetime has been more supportive of our great veterans than @POTUS.
